# Art Guide - Environment Configuration

# ==============================================================================
# Gemini API Configuration (Optional but Recommended)
# ==============================================================================
# Get your API key from: https://ai.google.dev/
# Without this key, the system uses placeholder descriptions
#
# GOOGLE_API_KEY=your_api_key_here

# Alternative environment variable names (any of these will work):
# GEMINI_API_KEY=your_api_key_here

# ==============================================================================
# Redis Configuration (For Distributed Mode)
# ==============================================================================
# REDIS_HOST=localhost
# REDIS_PORT=6379

# ==============================================================================
# Model Paths (Advanced - usually use defaults)
# ==============================================================================
# INDEX_PATH=models/faiss.index
# META_PATH=models/metadata.parquet

# ==============================================================================
# Notes:
# ==============================================================================
# - The system works WITHOUT Gemini API key (uses template descriptions)
# - To enable AI-generated descriptions, add GOOGLE_API_KEY above
# - For local development, copy this file to .env and add your key
# - For deployment, set environment variables in your hosting platform
